{
  "stem": "4830.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he has his word that if I don't write next year, they will not allow me to continue.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "At that time in Hungary, if I did not get further, there was no school that would have accepted me.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Already Jewish students could not get into public schools.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They could only go to the Jewish school, but there was only one Jewish gymnasium in Budapest, and there was a-- a much larger number of applicant.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were three schools in Budapest where they had Jewish classes, but these were separate as well.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So he called in my father and told him that, don't you think, Mr.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Cohen, that, in this day and age, in the year-- and this was in 1938-- it is anachronistic for a Jew not to write on Saturday when there are all these Jewish laws?",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And my father told him that I-- in my consideration, the Jewish laws are anachronistic, which made him to lose his patience.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He said, regardless what you think, if he's not writing, then he will not be accepted.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my father called me in to his room for a discussion.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He said a very important thing he wants to discuss with me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He said that he does not want to advise me, because it's up to my conscience, but he quoted different Talmudic quotations that, in case of the danger of life, the laws can be transgressed.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he said that, although this does not provide immediate danger, in a broad interpretation, if you are not studying and if you cannot finish your studies, then eventually you cannot make a living, then this is endangering you life.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But he doesn't want to advise me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But if I want to write, then he will not object.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
